|z|^2=z\bar{z}
k|z−z_1|=l|z−z_2|
k^2|z−z_1|^2=l^2|z−z_2|^2
k^2(z−z_1)(\bar{z}−\bar{z}_1)=l^2(z−z_2)(\bar{z}-\bar{z}_2)
(\frac{kl|z_1-z_2|}{|k^2-l^2|})^2
\frac{k^2z_1-l^2z_2}{k^2-l^2}
